1. Install homeshick (https://github.com/andsens/homeshick)
2. homesick clone tomazy/dotfiles


### Zsh

`brew install zsh zsh-completions zsh-history-substring-search`
`echo $(which zsh) | sudo tee -a /etc/shells`
`chsh -s $(which zsh)`

`npm install --global pure-prompt`

`chmod g-w /usr/local/share # on macOS`

